{"tid":1831081,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本寫明中國己有201人中左武漢肺炎3人死亡","createTime":"2020-01-20T06:36:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T10:13:01.000Z","uid":118550,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7d24f615384851e6a5a1d4b5abce4c34e8b00172","tid":1831081,"uid":118550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T06:36:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Sankei_news/status/1219030583101120514?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSankei_news%2Fstatus%2F1219030583101120514%3Fs%3D09&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9w8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=a479958e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSankei_news%2Fstatus%2F1219030583101120514%3Fs%3D09&h=63dbd3b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Sankei_news/status/1219030583101120514?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H15HkUG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH15HkUG.jpg&h=2f2ae041&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sankei.com/world/amp/200120/wor2001200002-a.html?__twitter_impression=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sankei.com%2Fworld%2Famp%2F200120%2Fwor2001200002-a.html%3F__twitter_impression%3Dtrue&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9w8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=f9c66d10\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sankei.com/world/amp/200120/wor2001200002-a.html?__twitter_impression=true</a><br />\n<br />\n中国湖北省武漢市の衛生当局は２０日、新型コロナウイルスによる肺炎で１人が死亡したと発表。死者は計３人となった。武漢の発症者は１３６人が新たに確認され、計１９８人になった。一方、中国メディアによると、北京市と広東省で２０日までに計３人の発症を確認。武漢以外の中国での発症確認は初めて。中国全体の発症者は計２０１人に達した。<br />\n<br />\n武漢市当局は「人から人への感染が続くリスクは比較的低く、予防、抑制は可能」としているが、中国は春節（旧正月）で人の移動が激しくなっており、各地で発症者が相次いで見つかる恐れもある。（共同）"},{"pid":"5d6a6aba4644f6ae109f19cefff29999ee2b342b","tid":1831081,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T06:37:24.000Z","msg":"期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"